title: Janelle Monae Prays Hollywood's Finally Waking Up (VIDEO)
text:
Janelle Monae Prays Hollywood's Finally Waking Up Janelle Monae Prays Hollywood's Finally Waking Up EXCLUSIVE 
Janelle Monae 's giving Hollywood props ... for belatedly listening. 
The " Moonlight " and " Hidden Figures " star arrived at LAX Wednesday and we asked if the Oscars were on the mark this year. 
Check it out ... Janelle -- who played major roles in both flicks that earned Oscar nominations -- gives a big thumbs up.
